msgid "I want to send an email, what should I do?"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/faq/faq.rst:302
msgid ""
"Basically, you need to add an email node and configure it. This node is "
"pre-configured to use the Gmail server ``gmail-smtp-in.l.google.com``, "
